pg
==

no more, no less, just a pager

usage
-----

To read a file:

	pg <file>

Inside pg, the following keys can be used:

	<Up>    j              scroll up   by one line
	<Down>  k              scroll down by one line
	<PgUp>  b              scroll up   by one page
	<PgDn>  f     <Space>  scroll down by one page
	g                      scroll to start of file
	G                      scroll to end   of file
	q       <C-c>          quit
	<[0-9]>                apply a numerical multiplier to the next
	                         command
